videos.description: David Duke stares down Eric Paschall after Duke's and-1 layup, but the Providence guard gets whistled for a technical foul for the taunt.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Providence's Duke gets tech after and-1 layup) 2019/02/13

videos.headline: Providence's Duke gets tech after and-1 layup

videos.description: Phil Booth blows by his defender and finishes with the flush for Villanova.
videos.headline: Booth soars for Villanova jam

videos.description: Alpha Diallo ignores the Villanova defense, then rolls baseline for the dunk plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Diallo drives baseline for nice Providence jam) 2019/02/13

videos.headline: Diallo drives baseline for nice Providence jam

videos.description: Dhamir Cosby-Roundtree gets the pass from Phil Booth, then hammers home a dunk plus the foul.
videos.headline: Cosby-Roundtree stuffs home and-1 dunk
